opennlp.ccg.util
Class Interner<T>

java.lang.Object
  opennlp.ccg.util.Interner<T>

public class Interner<T>
extends Object

A utility class for interning (canonicalizing) objects. A WeakHashMap is used as the backing store, so that interned objects can be garbage collected. Normally, it is easier to use the globalIntern method (sharing a global backing store) than to allocate separate interners. Individual interners can be constructed to use soft references to the interned objects, so that they are kept around longer than is the case with weak references (the default).
